'''保罗·德罗斯·博耶'''（{{lang-en|Paul Delos Boyer}}，{{bd|1918年|7月31日|2018年|6月2日|catIdx=Boyer}}），[[美国|美国]][[生物化学家|生物化学家]]。因阐明[[三磷酸腺苷|三磷酸腺苷]][[生物合成|生物合成]]的机理而与[[约翰·沃克|约翰·沃克]]、[[延斯·克里斯蒂安·斯科|延斯·克里斯蒂安·斯科]]共同获得1997年的[[诺贝尔化学奖|诺贝尔化学奖]]<ref>{{cite web|title=The Nobel Prize in Chemistry 1997|url=http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/chemistry/laureates/1997/|accessdate=2012-08-30|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618225859/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/chemistry/laureates/1997/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==逝世==
2018年6月2日，保羅·博耶因[[呼吸衰竭|呼吸衰竭]]而在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的自宅中辭世，享耆壽99歲<ref>{{cite web |last1=Wolpert |first1=Stuart |title=In memoriam: Paul Boyer, 99, Nobel laureate in chemistry |url=http://newsroom.ucla.edu/stories/in-memoriam:-paul-boyer-99-nobel-laureate-in-chemistry |website=UCLA Newsroom |publisher=University of California, Los Angeles |accessdate=2018-06-05 |date=2018-06-04 |archive-date=2018-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608110920/http://newsroom.ucla.edu/stories/in-memoriam:-paul-boyer-99-nobel-laureate-in-chemistry |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/paul-d-boyer-ucla-biochemist-who-won-nobel-prize-in-1997-dies-at-99/2018/06/06/3696323a-699b-11e8-9e38-24e693b38637_story.html?utm_term=.e84e420a38c7 |title=Paul D. Boyer, UCLA biochemist who won Nobel Prize in 1997, dies at 99 |accessdate=2018-06-07 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612144025/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/paul-d-boyer-ucla-biochemist-who-won-nobel-prize-in-1997-dies-at-99/2018/06/06/3696323a-699b-11e8-9e38-24e693b38637_story.html?utm_term=.e84e420a38c7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

